Package: rk8s
Type: Package
Title: Kubernetes Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", email = "iflores.siaca@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R client for the Kubernetes API, providing access to typed
    resource APIs (Core, Apps, Batch, Networking, RBAC, ...) and a dynamic
    client for custom resources. Mirrors the design of the official
    Kubernetes Python client and Go client-go: a hand-written runtime
    (configuration, authentication, watch, streaming, dynamic client) plus
    typed API and model classes code-generated from the Kubernetes OpenAPI
    specification.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/ian-flores/rk8s
BugReports: https://github.com/ian-flores/rk8s/issues
